**Año**: Not specified
**Journal**: Progress in Neuropsychopharmacology & Biological Psychiatry, 90 (2018) 134-141. doi:10.1016/j.pnpbp.2018.11.012
**DOI/Link**: Magnesium; ADHD; Trace element; Nutrition; Meta-analysis; 

